{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_19041.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303201,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Mayu","nameRight":"Asuka","textLeft":"In order to prove that Ria isn't the@thief...","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":303201}],"textLeft":"I have to find either her or the Witch."},{"chara":[{"id":101301}],"textRight":"Mayu, you really believe Ria is innocent,@don't you?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303201}],"textLeft":"Yes."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303201}],"textLeft":"She always helps me when I'm in trouble."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303201,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"Like that time..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21021.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story03","chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303201,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":1}],"nameCenter":"Mayu","nameLeft":"Mayu","nameRight":"Ria","textCenter":"It's gone... Wh-what should I do?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":303201,"pos":0}],"nameNarration":"Mayu","narration":"The memento of my father who passed away@when I was little. The only thing I owned that@was filled with my few memories of him...","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narration":"When I lost that precious pendant of mine,@the one person who was there for me..."},{"chara":[{"id":301001}],"narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"Mayu? What are you doing?"},{"chara":[{"id":303201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Ria..."},{"nameNarration":"Mayu","narration":"...was Ria.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21028.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"How about over there?","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"No... It's not here either."},{"chara":[{"id":303201}],"textLeft":"Um, Ria... It's getting late."},{"chara":[{"id":303201,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"I can look for it by myself now."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":1}],"textRight":"Don't be silly. It's important to you, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301001}],"textRight":"Someone as easygoing as you could never find@it without any help."},{"chara":[{"id":303201}],"textLeft":"Maybe, but..."},{"chara":[{"id":301001}],"textRight":"Anyhow, I already offered to help."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001}],"textRight":"There's nothing beautiful about giving up@halfway."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303201,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"Ria..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":400}],"textRight":"Come on, now! Let's keep looking!"},{"bg":"bg_adv_12083.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"textRight":"Here it is! I found it! [chara:301001:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:301001:cheek_0][chara:301001:face_mtn_ex_010.exp.json][chara:301001:lipSynch_1]This is it, right?","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"effect":"slideInLeftFast","face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"Ah! It is! That's it!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303201,"motion":100,"tear":1}],"textLeft":"Thank you... Ria, thank you so much."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0}],"textRight":"I'm happy we found it!"},{"chara":[{"id":303201}],"textLeft":"Yes... You're incredible, Ria."},{"chara":[{"id":303201}],"textLeft":"You aren't just beautiful and charming.@You're also dependable..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301001,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"...?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":100}],"textRight":"[chara:301001:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]Of course! This is to be expected when you@enlist the help of someone as perfect as I!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303201,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"bg":"bg_adv_19041.jpg","chara":[{"id":303201}],"nameLeft":"Mayu","nameRight":"Asuka","textLeft":"Even when I was starting to give up, even@after the sun set and it got dark...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":303201}],"textLeft":"Ria continued to help me search until we@found the pendant."},{"chara":[{"id":303201,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"Because she knew how important it was to me."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Someone that kind..."},{"chara":[{"id":303201}],"textLeft":"...would never steal someone else's treasure!"},{"chara":[{"id":101301}],"textRight":"Er, yes, I suppose."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101301,"motion":0}],"textRight":"After hearing that, I find it hard to believe@she could be the thief."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303201,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"[chara:303201:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]So you believe in her too!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101301,"motion":100}],"textRight":"S-still! It's also true that she was@wandering around the crime scenes!"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303201,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101301,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"[chara:101301:effect_ef_adv_01][se:7201_detect_magic][chara:303201:effect_ef_adv_01][se:7201_detect_magic]...?!"},{"chara":[{"id":101301}],"textRight":"Is this?!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_47001.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"enterWitchSpace","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":101301},{"effect":"fadeout","id":303201}],"se":"7208_wander_into","textClear":1},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime12","chara":[{"id":7001,"name":"sprite_0","pos":1}],"nameCenter":"","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"[flashEffect:flashWhite2][bgEffect:shakeSmall]＄・＃＄＆＃!!!SHLー！"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":7001,"name":"sprite_0"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303201,"motion":400,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"textLeft":"[bgEffect:shakeLarge]Ahhh!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101301}],"textRight":"Mayu!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"I'm okay! I managed to dodge it!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101301}],"textRight":"That's all that matters!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"ef_adv_05","face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101300,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"se":"7205_magic_girl","textRight":"Okay then, here I go!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"ef_adv_05","face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"se":"7205_magic_girl","textLeft":"Ah, me too... I may not be strong, but I'll@do what I can!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}